    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1894-03-12T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1894-03-12T00:00:00-05:00" n="161"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d161">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Thompson</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Gresham</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Legation of the United States</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Rio de Janeiro</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1894-03-12">
                            <hi rend="italic">March 12, 1894</hi>
                        </date>. (Received March 12.)</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Mr. Thompson transmits the information given him by the chargé d’affaires of
                    Portugal, that asylum was asked by and granted to Da Gama on the preceding day,
                    on board the <hi rend="italic">Mindello</hi>, a Portuguese war vessel.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
